                        user interfaces and experiences for Android
                        applications. It involves designing intuitive and
                        visually appealing interfaces that enhance user
                        interaction and satisfaction on Android devices. UX
                        design focuses on understanding user behavior and
                        preferences to create seamless and enjoyable
                        experiences, while UI design focuses on the visual
                        aspects of the interface, including layout, typography,
                        colors, and interactive elements.
                      </p>
                    </div>
